Cal lightman sees the truth.

00:40.301 --> 00:42.501
It's written
all over your face.

00:42.568 --> 00:44.934
It's also in your voice,
your posture,

00:45.000 --> 00:46.534
The words you choose.

00:46.600 --> 00:49.401
Because of dr. lightman's
scientific discoveries,

00:49.468 --> 00:51.367
We know that these signs
are the same...

00:51.434 --> 00:53.234
Laying it on
a bit thick,
isn't she?

00:53.301 --> 00:55.367
It's called
selling books, dad.
shut up and bask.

00:55.434 --> 00:57.167
Now, give him 5 minutes
and 20 questions,

00:57.234 --> 01:00.534
And he'll know whether
you went off to argentina
to cheat on your wife,

01:00.600 --> 01:03.733
Lied about
a well-timed stock sale,

01:03.800 --> 01:06.434
Or murdered
a one-night stand.

01:06.501 --> 01:09.568
Ladies and gentlemen,
please join me in welcoming

01:09.633 --> 01:12.201
The world's foremost
deception expert

01:12.267 --> 01:14.034
And one of america's
preeminent scientists,

01:14.101 --> 01:17.600
<i>author of lies we tell,
dr. cal lightman.</i>

01:17.667 --> 01:20.434
[applause]

01:22.667 --> 01:26.367
Well, she's right
when she says i'll know
if you're lying,

01:26.434 --> 01:29.534
But what
i wanna know is why.

01:29.600 --> 01:31.667
That's still
your secret.

01:31.733 --> 01:33.501
Any questions?

01:33.568 --> 01:34.733
Dr. lightman.

01:37.167 --> 01:38.334
Thanks for coming.

01:40.034 --> 01:43.568
How come no one ever
looks me in the eye
at these things?

01:45.800 --> 01:47.134
Oh, cool tattoo.

01:47.201 --> 01:48.434
Who do
i make it out to?

01:48.501 --> 01:49.733
Uh, trisha, please.

01:50.967 --> 01:53.201
You're really the world's
biggest expert on lying?

01:53.267 --> 01:55.967
When he's
not being a dad or
a big-time author.

01:56.034 --> 01:59.000
So you'll know
i'm telling the truth.

01:59.067 --> 02:02.101
The police don't believe me.
no one does. i--

02:02.167 --> 02:05.201
I just really need
someone to believe me.

02:07.101 --> 02:09.334
I saw a murder.

02:10.366 --> 02:13.367
I didn't "see it" see it,
but i saw it

02:13.434 --> 02:16.568
In a vision,
a psychic vision,

02:16.633 --> 02:18.767
But i know
it really happened.

02:20.967 --> 02:23.733
Am i telling the truth?

02:26.767 --> 02:28.633
Yes, you are.

02:28.700 --> 02:32.167
Captioning made possible by
20th century fox

02:32.234 --> 02:36.167
Ryan star: * dream,
send me a sign *

02:36.234 --> 02:38.767
* turn back the clock *

02:38.834 --> 02:40.934
* give me some time *

02:41.000 --> 02:43.900
* i need to break out *

02:43.967 --> 02:46.101
* and make a new name *

02:46.167 --> 02:48.733
* let's open our eyes *

02:48.800 --> 02:55.733
